com.csm.rover.simulator.objects

Class ThreadItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.csm.rover.simulator.objects.ThreadItem

  • public class ThreadItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This object is used as a wrapper for managing synchronous threads. It tracks whether a thread is running, complete, or suspended and when it has permission to run.

    • Constructor Detail

      • ThreadItem

        public ThreadItem(java.lang.String name,
                  int delay,
                  long start,
                  SynchronousThread thread)
        Creates a new tracker for the provided thread. The other parameters are used to identify when the thread should have run permission.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the thread
        delay - The time the thread should sleep between executions
        start - The current time, the time the thread should start counting from
        thread - The thread being handled by the ThreadItem
